                    <ab>
                        <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/37"
                            >Rodulfus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Emperor/king">rex</rs>, dietro la supplica di <persName
                            key="#Bishops" ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/45">Lantpertus
                            Mediolanensis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">archiepiscopus</rs> et <persName key="#Bishops"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/78">Adalbertus</persName> sanctae
                        sedis Bergamensis <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs> et <persName
                            key="#Marquis/duke" ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/23"
                            >Bonefacius</persName>
                        <rs key="#Marquis/duke">marchio</rs>, concede e conferma al monastero
                        fondato dall’<rs key="#Queen">imperatrice</rs>
                        <persName key="#Queen" ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/55"
                            >Angelberga</persName> e dedicato da <persName key="#Abbesses"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/67">Berta</persName> a <orgName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/juridical_persons/53">S. Sisto</orgName>
                        <geogName ref="#http://137.204.128.125/estates/40"
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property">quasdam <rs
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property">curtes</rs>
                            <placeName key="#Curtes" ref="http://137.204.128.125/places/33"
                                >Vuardestallam</placeName>
                        </geogName> scilicet, <geogName key=""
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/estates/77">
                            <placeName key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property"
                                ref="http://137.204.128.125/places/32">Luzariam</placeName>
                        </geogName>, <geogName key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/estates/77">Litora Paludiana</geogName>,
                            <geogName ref="#http://137.204.128.125/estates/80">Villolę</geogName>,
                            <geogName key="" ref="#http://137.204.128.125/estates/42">
                            <placeName key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property"
                                ref="http://137.204.128.125/places/34">Piguniarius</placeName>
                        </geogName>, e tutte le cose che la predetta imperatrice trasferì al
                        cenobio. Il monastero è affidato a Berta che ne sarà dominatrix, ordinatrix
                        atque retrix. Concediamo tutti i <rs key="#Landed_possessions">possessi
                            mobiles ac immobiles</rs>, tam per <rs key="#Parchment_documents"
                            >cartulas</rs> quamque extra cartulas o pervenuti a qualsiasi altro
                        titolo, acquisiti o da acquisire, tutto quello che è stato concesso dagli
                        imperatori, atque <rs key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property">cellulam</rs> quandam
                        que antiquitus monasterium dicebatur non procul a <placeName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/43">Placentina urbe</placeName>
                        sitam, loco qui <geogName key="#Fiscal_Property #Curtes #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/estates/76"><placeName
                                ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/14">Caput
                            Trebiae</placeName></geogName> vocatur, che era stata data da <persName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/80" key="#Emperor/king"
                            >Carlomanno</persName> al monastero <rs
                            key="#Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure">proprietario iure</rs>. <rs
                            key="#Personal_statuses">Familias quoque utriusque sexus et
                            conditionis</rs> cum <rs key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property">curtibus</rs> et
                            <rs key="#Churches/religious_bodies">cappellis</rs> e segue l’elenco di
                        tutte le appendici. Per chiunque violerà gli accordi, pena di £150 d’oro,
                        metà da pagare camerę nostre, metà a Berta.SM Rodulfi piissimi
                            regis.<persName>Manno</persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarius</rs> ad vicem venerabilis Beati episcopi
                        et <rs key="#Archchancellor">archicancellarii</rs> rec. et sub. Data. Actum
                            <placeName ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/59">Veronę</placeName>,
                        in Christi nomine feliciter, amen.</ab>
